{"tid":933405,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[互動故]連登建國","createTime":"2018-12-08T13:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T09:39:22.000Z","uid":221544,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e350216b0f191dab8892a73eaad4b34edf824734","tid":933405,"uid":221544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T13:49:44.000Z","msg":"權力，是大多數人所渴望的。<br />\n這天，你在選舉中勝出，成為新一任的市長。<br />\n<br />\n你會帶這座城市走向繁榮 ，還是會把這城市步向衰落？<br />\n這都是你的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n首先請選擇你的城市的名稱"},{"pid":"27ed86bac5de662f59c262ca17be957297885301","tid":933405,"uid":218794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T13:50:28.000Z","msg":"終國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21ffa34cb1d17bc8a225bfe9372606abccc0875","tid":933405,"uid":221544,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T13:50:41.000Z","msg":"部分背景資料<br />\n你的城市地圖如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ZBD5ZN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ZBD5ZN.png&h=be367cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南區為目前已發展地區<br />\n東區為大型基建的聚集地(機場,港口等）<br />\n北區擁有豐富天然資源 <br />\n<br />\n人口 總共200萬<br />\n 勞動人口為120萬<br />\n 18歲以下人口有50萬 <br />\n<br />\n經濟狀況 <br />\n以輕工業為主<br />\n佔GDP 55% <br />\n庫房 2000億 港元 (除非特別情況，否則貨幣一律爲港元 )<br />\n<br />\n目前社會議題<br />\n南區污染問題 <br />\n勞工薪金過低 <br />\n醫療設施不足 <br />\n<br />\n其他會隨著故事發展透露"},{"pid":"2d8ce034af4b42b7ab9c41d8b89c8bbbd3a60930","tid":933405,"uid":221544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T13:52:01.000Z","msg":"你的城市名稱為 終國<br />\n請問你的名字是？"},{"pid":"49897c9a7a30469484921375b0e78b300ecd754c","tid":933405,"uid":218794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T13:52:38.000Z","msg":"扎更平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697a50760e2000f99a357a05775147f2641f9b4f","tid":933405,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci